# Legacy / alternate path aliases. Permanent (301) so search engines
# consolidate ranking signals to the canonical URLs and don't index
# duplicate content. We do NOT have a /* catch-all; Cloudflare Pages
# will serve /404.html with HTTP 404 for anything not matched above
# or by a static file.
/privacy-policy          /privacy        301
/terms-of-service        /terms          301
/accessibility-statement /accessibility  301
/cookies                 /privacy        301
/cookie-policy           /privacy        301
